  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1055">
<l>karappilār vaiyakat tuṇmaiyāṟ kaṇṇiṉ</l>
<l>ṟirappavar mēṟkoḷ vatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As there are in the world those that give without refusing, there are (also) those that prefer to beg by simply standing before them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
